-♪ And after all ♪
-♪ After all ♪

36:13.125 --> 36:19.000
-♪ The rain will fall on us two ♪
-♪ Rain will fall on us two ♪

36:19.083 --> 36:22.208
-♪ But I'll keep moving on ♪
-♪ Moving on ♪

36:22.291 --> 36:26.791
-♪ For I am strong with you ♪
-♪ With you ♪

36:27.833 --> 36:31.083
♪ With you ♪

36:31.166 --> 36:34.708
[footsteps approaching]

36:34.791 --> 36:36.083
[door opens]

36:36.583 --> 36:39.750
-♪ Our love ♪
-♪ Is a bourbon fountain ♪

36:39.833 --> 36:42.125
♪ Bourbon fountain, yeah ♪

36:42.208 --> 36:46.500
-♪ That floats into the sea ♪
-♪ Floats into the sea ♪

36:46.583 --> 36:49.000
♪ Deeper than any ocean ♪

36:51.291 --> 36:55.458
-♪ For eternity ♪
-♪ For eternity ♪

36:55.541 --> 36:59.125
♪ Yeah ♪

